{"tid":1607502,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"(國際戰線) 請英文人貼去Reddit,宣布十一香港戒嚴","createTime":"2019-10-01T00:46:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T03:13:23.000Z","uid":41458,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ef539d4007d6e5fd4c112668de387fac94348771","tid":1607502,"uid":41458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T00:46:45.000Z","msg":"香港主要鐵路站關閉<br />\n大部分商場關閉<br />\n解放軍同黑警守係主要道路，任意截查拘捕平民<br />\n<br />\n香港實際就係戒嚴，必須向國際宣揚！！！<br />\n唔係外國會以為香港示威規模減少！！！"},{"pid":"c6997f29acf80f8d0dd80bd67b91efce8908e807","tid":1607502,"uid":41458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T00:48:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8ebfe0ac696e60ecdb92e3f9f2e21b5d82bb56b","tid":1607502,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T02:06:48.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">六區開花要對準政權，梗係去議員辦事處賀佢老母啦</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔好再</span></strong></span>企起街上面<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>圍警局</strong></span></span>，分區活動就應該<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>打游擊戰去搵該區既建制派議員</strong></span></span>同佢地開party一齊賀一賀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，至於邊一區去邊間就大家自己衡量下喇﹗<br />\n<br />\n屯門區區議員<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%B1%AF%E9%96%80%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E5%25B1%25AF%25E9%2596%2580%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%2583&d=Cf%2FvPHDuk0dzuxx%2BuF7CdY429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=c78ad36b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%B1%AF%E9%96%80%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83</a><br />\n荃灣區議員<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%8D%83%E7%81%A3%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E8%258D%2583%25E7%2581%25A3%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%2583&d=Cf%2FvPHDuk0dzuxx%2BuF7CdY429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=3243fb5f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%8D%83%E7%81%A3%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83</a><br />\n沙田區議員<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%B2%99%E7%94%B0%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E6%25B2%2599%25E7%2594%25B0%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%2583&d=Cf%2FvPHDuk0dzuxx%2BuF7CdY429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=b4580ba1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%B2%99%E7%94%B0%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83</a><br />\n黃大仙區議員<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%BB%83%E5%A4%A7%E4%BB%99%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E9%25BB%2583%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E4%25BB%2599%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%2583&d=Cf%2FvPHDuk0dzuxx%2BuF7CdY429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=3068b31a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%BB%83%E5%A4%A7%E4%BB%99%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83</a><br />\n深水埗區議員<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%B7%B1%E6%B0%B4%E5%9F%97%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E6%25B7%25B1%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E5%259F%2597%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%2583&d=Cf%2FvPHDuk0dzuxx%2BuF7CdY429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=c9782032\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%B7%B1%E6%B0%B4%E5%9F%97%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83</a><br />\n灣仔區議員<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%81%A3%E4%BB%94%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E7%2581%25A3%25E4%25BB%2594%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%2583&d=Cf%2FvPHDuk0dzuxx%2BuF7CdY429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=7799d1fa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%81%A3%E4%BB%94%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1.打電話（呢個係每日都可以做既）</span></span></strong><br />\n打電話搵議員(之前有巴打post過出黎，可以自己搵下)問下國慶期間區內有咩最新活動、巴士路線、有咩醫生診所好介紹呀等等，電話打唔通既whatsapp都可以，無whatsapp既巴絲打可以send email去，連email都無既可以fax過去查詢下，無人應既話可以搵下無限fax大法fax到佢應機為止。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>2.連儂牆</strong></span></span><br />\n都係搵立法會議員/區議員辦事處啦，無開門既咪留張紙起度寫低自己有咩問或者有咩訴求囉。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>3.裝修</strong></span></span><br />\n有好多議員都扎根起屋邨做左好耐，裡面啲裝修又殘又舊，有心既手足可以襯國慶幫佢地補下油、翻新下添置返少少國慶節日既氣氛，用咩色就自己決定啦。<br />\n補充:好多office既出入口好窄，大家入office查詢既時候動作唔好太大呀，唔小心撞到佢地d玻璃就大鑊喇。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>4.餵office既龜龜食野(蟲系魔法師出動)</strong></span></span><br />\n巴絲打們都可以準備少少紅蟲、蚯蚓、生雞蛋、甜野呀個d比入面既龜龜食，可以吸引到更多蟲蟲輕易大量繁殖既就更好。大家知啦，議員們公事繁忙，萬一無時間餵佢地，龜龜都仲有少少野食丫嘛。<br />\n補充：拉開櫃桶餵既時候記住小心啲，唔好倒瀉手上罐可樂呀，會惹到成地蟻架！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>原post:</strong></span><br />\n國慶咁大件事 緊係要約埋建制議員賀佢老母<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1605409\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1605409</a>"},{"pid":"d2102f38af49830933b509e798dee3ff1c160bb3","tid":1607502,"uid":134054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T02:09:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">10月1日手足要黑衫攝衫<br />\n一人一支漂白水反攻<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一人一個鎖 狗鐵一封站就反鎖狗入面<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">要比多啲人睇到<br />\n10月1號熄燈嘅時候<br />\n係去Twitter<br />\n#LIHKG101<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n快啲幫手share<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ba43c0efb476752f93a14ba46d8a70c5c4e6130","tid":1607502,"uid":41458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T03:59:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f77fe0fdaf09d4f8520f7620d37327ce3251860b","tid":1607502,"uid":306208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T04:12:33.000Z","msg":"呢個要推呀！"},{"pid":"bf77e8aee04098c97743916130a0e840d4d36dec","tid":1607502,"uid":41458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T04:16:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"480bc34a0744a5e35bd6c3a06ca3033ac6db55c1","tid":1607502,"uid":248290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T04:23:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum